{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act40side", "eventName": "相見歡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OR-ST-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "陳皮菊花茶", "storyInfo": "四十年前，真龍去世的消息使得整個炎國上下震動。在晚春的雨夜，匆匆離開百灶城的，有一位皇子，還有一位攜家帶口的書生。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$midautumn", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chess"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "先生是說，大炎歷史上當真有這麼一位奇人？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "收錄書卷，整理文字，推廣教育……為何她為天下蒼生做了這麼多事，卻沒有人記得她，甚至沒有人知道她的名字？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "先生，這是什麼字？我似乎從來沒有見過？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "並非無人記得“她”，只是她的一字真名，沒有被史書記錄在冊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這樣豈不可惜？明明她的筆寫下了炎國悠久的歷史，寫遍了炎國萬里的山河，可史書中沒有一頁留下了她的名字……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "您說……如果我把這些史書盡數補全，能從中還原出她的模樣嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "四十年前", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>1062年4月21日    穀雨</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客人，客人！", "name": "吆喝的夥計"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼大的雨，進來喝壺熱茶，避避雨再走吧。", "name": "吆喝的夥計"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必了。這場雨眼看著一時半刻也停不下來，還是快些趕路吧。", "name": "沉穩的男性"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，有人盼著這場雨停下，可還有人盼著它多下一陣啊。", "name": "吆喝的夥計"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賣傘的商販笑開花，就是苦了趕路人。", "name": "吆喝的夥計"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下說的話倒是有趣……", "name": "沉穩的男性"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客人還是歇歇腳吧。有人託我囑咐您，前路坑窪不好走，怕您踏錯沾濕了鞋。", "name": "吆喝的夥計"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……？", "name": "沉穩的男性"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客人，這邊請吧，要見您的那位已經在裡面等著了。", "name": "吆喝的夥計"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g13_yanlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.15, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尚書大人……好久不見。", "name": "朔"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，現在應該稱您為……太傅。", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門一別，的確很久不見了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為這次回京述職，應該要先見司歲台和兵部才對。", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我才趕在那之前來見你一面。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……陛下駕崩了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何時……？", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半月前。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想……如果陛下是壽終正寢，太傅也不會專程來見我。", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道……", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坐在陰影中的人伸出手，他的掌心，正躺著一枚黑色棋子。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "六十年前，他逃離了那座古寺，將自己化作一百八十一顆黑子，分散各地，至今下落不明。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而就在半月前，司歲台在京城發現了這一枚黑子的蹤跡。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他做了什麼？", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尚不知曉……", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一可以確定的是，他絕無可能進入禁城……應是有人主動見了他。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個人的身分，不方便去查。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想做的事，按理不該牽扯到旁人才是……", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天我本不該見你。可當初那個罪人引起動亂時，畢竟是你親手將他制伏的。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……宗師，對此事，你知道什麼嗎？", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……並無所知。", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那次事故之後，我也沒有再見過他。", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我相信宗師。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要我做些什麼嗎？", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要停留，即刻返回玉門。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏薩斯動蕩不斷，玉門守將新舊交替，這個時間，切不可再使人心動蕩。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "司歲台與兵部，我自會處理。你不在局中，我才能以重任相託。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……明白。", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棋局之事，我會讓司歲台暗中繼續查下去。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特殊時期，宗師不便再露面——你可以當今日沒有見過我。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真龍他究竟是……炎武殿下還好嗎？", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個時候，他應該——", "name": "朔"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎武……", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下去世的那天晚上，是炎武去見了他。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g5_dragonpalace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-30", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啟稟殿下，那叛臣一族二十八人皆已收監。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可核對名錄時發現，其家中本應有一個尚不滿月的嬰兒——", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是禁軍今天在太師府中搜查時，將整個宅子翻了個底朝天，也沒有找到那嬰兒的下落。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……一個還在襁褓裡的孩子，總不會是自己逃走的。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是有人惦記著她。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下不必煩擾，禁軍會找到她。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天早些時候，刑部尚書求見。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一系列的案子，到底該怎麼審怎麼辦，他想徵求殿下的意見。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……依炎律審。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會轉告他。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的那位兄長，現在到何處了？", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據守軍報告，半個時辰前剛出京城。有部分禁軍追隨他叛逃。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守城士兵未得軍令，不敢阻攔。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊……我的確沒有下過要將他留在百灶的命令。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是他不願意留下，棄了所有人而去了。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟著他走的禁軍……有多少人？", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十八人。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這位兄長，就算犯下了這樣的滔天罪行，還是可以讓太師替他赴死，還是可以讓這十八死士願意追隨他而去。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這滿朝文武，還有多少人的心在他那裡？有多少人，還在盼望他回來坐這個位置？", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可如今，是殿下在這個位置。讓炎國萬世昌寧的責任，也在殿下身上。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#2$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎國上下，任誰都可以心思徘徊，猶疑不定……唯獨殿下您不行。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有許久沒有走出這座宮殿了……太尉，告訴我——", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "百灶的這場春雨，停了嗎？", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要殿下想，這場雨就可以停下。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……若殿下改了主意，還來得及將他們留下。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……乏了。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "御膳司備了些八寶攢湯和筍絲，殿下可要用點？", "name": "侍從"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起菜吧。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,-30", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_rain", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_carriage_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "b", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_babycry_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 2.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乖……乖……", "name": "溫柔的女性"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不哭不哭，我們回家去……就快要到家了……", "name": "溫柔的女性"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再快些……勞駕，麻煩您再快些……", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼大的雨，路都看不清，不能再快啦……", "name": "車夫"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離下一個驛站還有多遠？", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼也得三十里地吧……", "name": "車夫"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位兄弟，您是有多要緊的事……拖家帶口的，怎麼就偏挑這麼個晚上趕路啊？", "name": "車夫"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#4$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請快些吧。", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#2$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1634_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.9}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……！啊！什麼東西——", "name": "車夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1634_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pcknmgrwl"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見鬼了！這荒郊野外的，怎麼還有活人啊……", "name": "車夫"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#7$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人四下張望，綿延不絕的雨幕遮住了視線，夜色茫茫，什麼都看不到。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可以再乘車了……", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_goldcoin", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞駕，這些錢都留給您。請把車駛到前面的驛站去，要是有人問起的話，千萬不要說今晚拉過帶著孩子的客人。", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#5$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在下拜謝先生……", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……這，唉！", "name": "車夫"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼大的雨，您要上哪去啊？", "name": "車夫"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從小路走……穿過北邊的林子——", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#3$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——！", "name": "驚慌的女性"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了——", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#8$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子……", "name": "驚慌的女性"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子不見了……", "name": "驚慌的女性"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1616_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "倉皇的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1616_1#6$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g11_yanroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$midautumn", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#2$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是……那個孩子。", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#2$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "襁褓中的嬰兒睡得香甜，臉蛋上沾染了泥污與血汙也渾然不覺。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#2$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您交代我辦的事，我都已經辦成了……", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的手段，我都清楚，也知道該怎麼應付。大人不必擔憂，我絕不會讓半點血沾在您的身上。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生大義……老朽無以為報。", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……您不該謝我，我不是為您才做這件事的。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位大人曾有大恩於我。我做的這件事，卻不能為她洗淨冤屈，甚至連為她報仇都談不上。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有親人，不用操心身後事。想拜託大人的，也就只有這一件事。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人……請您收養這個孩子吧。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#3$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不必告訴她什麼，只要讓她平安長大，安穩地活過這一輩子就好了。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你知道，她留在這裡，就多一分風險，多一分將這樁舊案重新翻出來的可能。", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可這難道不是您盼望的嗎？", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時勢使然，現在我們注定無可奈何。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是總有一天，不管三十年也好，四十年也好……只要有朝一日，真相能大白於天下……", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些血……就不算白流。", "name": "滿手血汙的人"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#2$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我答應你。", "name": "沉默的老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}